headline: Stryker unveils Oculan Lighting Platform to enhance surgical visualization and illumination
summary: Stryker (NYSE: SYK), a global leader in medical technologies, unveiled the Oculan Lighting Platform, an innovative lighting solution designed to provide consistent, high-quality illumination, allowing surgeons to focus on delivering the highest standard of care.
